data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Southgate! This fabulous 4 bedroom, 2 full bath brick ranch with garage & finished basement is ready to make all your homeownership dreams come true. Step inside and be greeted by the warm embrace of natural light that floods in through the windows, illuminating the spacious living room that has plush new carpet!! The updated kitchen features new flooring, a tile backsplash and beautiful cabinetry with plenty of drawers! All appliances stay including the new gas range!! The adjacent dining area also has new flooring!! Need some extra space? No problem! This home boasts a finished basement with plenty of room to entertain, ample storage and the second full bath! When it's time to unwind, retreat to one of the four generously sized bedrooms all with new carpet!! Outside, a well-maintained backyard awaits, perfect for hosting summer gatherings or simply enjoying a quiet evening under the stars. The brick exterior, windows and newer roof of the house give it timeless charm, adding an extra touch of character and curb appeal to this already incredible home. Keep the front yard grass green with the sprinkler system (front yard only). The garage is easy to access with a garage door opener! Located in the desirable city of Southgate, this property is nestled in a neighborhood with easy access to schools, parks, shopping, and all the amenities you could ask for. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your forever home.
